# LS Commerce GmbH – Portfolio Website

## Project Overview
Single-page portfolio website for **LS Commerce GmbH**, a Swiss digital commerce company.
- **Stack**: React, Vite, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS v4, shadcn/ui, lucide-react
- **Language**: German only – all UI text in German
- **Design**: Swiss minimalism – clean, quiet, lots of whitespace

## Design System

### Colors (matches VexaMiner / vexa-flasher brand)
- Background: white (`bg-white`)
- Text primary: `text-zinc-900` (weight 400–500)
- Text secondary: `text-zinc-500` / `text-zinc-600`
- Primary accent: `#f97627` (orange-600) – used for section titles, icons, buttons, highlights
- Orange scale: `orange-400` through `orange-600` for interactive elements
- Borders/dividers: `border-zinc-100` or `border-zinc-200`
- No gradients. No bright colors outside the orange accent palette.

### Typography
- System font stack (default Tailwind)
- Section titles: 13px, uppercase, tracking-widest, `text-[#f97627]`
- Body text: 16px, font-normal, relaxed leading
- Max content width: `max-w-[1100px]` centered

### Spacing
- Very large section padding: `py-28` minimum
- Generous gaps between elements
- Sections separated by thin zinc-100 borders

### Components
- Use shadcn/ui components – import from `@/components/ui/*`
- No rounded corners on custom elements (cards, inputs, buttons use `rounded-none`)
- Cards: no shadow, thin border, white background
- Buttons: `rounded-none`, `bg-orange-600 hover:bg-orange-500`, white text

### Layout
- Single page with scrolling sections
- Sticky header with thin bottom border
- Max width 1100px, centered with `mx-auto`
- Responsive: mobile-first, grid collapses gracefully

## Code Conventions

### Imports
- Use `@/` path alias for all src imports
- shadcn components: `@/components/ui/[component]`
- Custom components: `@/components/[Component]`

### Component Style
- Named exports for components (no default except App)
- Functional components only
- Props typed inline or with explicit interface
- Keep components focused – one section per file

### Files
- Components in `src/components/`
- UI primitives in `src/components/ui/` (managed by shadcn)
- Utilities in `src/lib/`

## Content Rules
- All text in German exactly as specified
- No stock photos of people
- No product images
- No specific brand names
- No founder/team information
- Professional, neutral Swiss tech company tone
- No SEO fluff or marketing buzzwords

## Restrictions
- No animations except optional soft fade on scroll
- No dark mode (light only)
- No slideshows or carousels
- No external API calls (contact form logs to console)
- No router needed – single page with anchor scrolling
